<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Chart Area Grid Configuration Demo</Bold>-This sample illustrates the entire chart area grid proerty configuration within a chart control.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14" > <Bold>Multiple Chart Areas Demo</Bold>-This sample illustrates having multiple chart areas within a chart control.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"> <Bold>SyncChartAreas Demo</Bold>-Demonstrates the Synchronization of chart areas with a single primary axis.</Paragraph>
